Type: Package
Package: viewseurat
Title: Interactive Shiny Dashboard for Viewing Seurat Objects
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cantalupo", "Paul", , "pcantalupo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive R Shiny dashboard for exploring Seurat v4 and
    v5 single-cell RNA-seq objects. Provides comprehensive graphical views
    of all components within a Seurat object including assays, reductions,
    metadata, graphs, and spatial images without performing additional
    analysis. Use ViewSeurat() to view objects directly from R, or run the
    app standalone to upload files via browser.
